## UI primitives — @ajh/ui only

Never use raw `<button>`, `<select>`, `<textarea>` in features/, routes/, or components/.

```tsx
// ❌ BANNED by ESLint
<button onClick={fn}>Click</button>

// ✅
import { Button } from '@ajh/ui';
<Button onClick={fn}>Click</Button>
```

Full primitive map:

| Need | Import |
|------|--------|
| Button | `import { Button } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Input | `import { Input } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Textarea | `import { TextArea } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Dropdown | `import { SelectDropdown } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Modal | `import { ModalShell } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Confirm | `import { ConfirmModal } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Empty state | `import { EmptyState } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Error state | `import { ErrorState } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Skeletons | `import { RowSkeleton, CardSkeleton } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Card | `import { GlassCard } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Settings card | `import { SettingsSection } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Tile | `import { OptionTile } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| AI stream | `import { StreamingText } from '@ajh/ui'` |
| Page wrapper | `import { PageShell } from '@/components/layout/PageShell'` |
| App banner | `import { UpdateBanner } from '@/components/ui/UpdateBanner'` |

Allowed raw exceptions: `<input type="range|file|checkbox|radio|hidden">`.

