## Design system

```tsx
// ❌ BANNED
className="text-[#c084fc] bg-[#a855f7]/15"
transition={{ duration: 0.18 }}

// ✅
className="text-brand-soft bg-brand/15"
import { transition } from '@/lib/motion';
transition={transition.normal}
```

---

## Package boundaries

```ts
// ❌ BANNED in renderer
import { x } from '@ajh/core';
import { x } from '@ajh/data';
import { x } from '@ajh/ai';
import { x } from '@ajh/workers';
```

---

## Data fetching

No `useState + useEffect` for remote data. Every IPC call has a service hook in `@/services/`.

---

## Cross-feature isolation

Features must not import from each other's internal directories:
```ts
// ❌ feature A importing feature B's internal component
import { SomeComponent } from '../settings/components/SomeComponent';
```

Shared logic belongs in `@ajh/ui`, `@/components/layout/`, `@/hooks/`, or `@/lib/`.

